  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[On Play] Reveal the top 4 cards of your deck. Add 1 red
    Digimon card with [Vaccine] in its traits among them to your hand. Place the
    rest at the bottom of your deck in any order.[Your Turn] When you play a red
    Digimon with [Avian], [Bird], [Beast], [Animal], or [Sovereign] in its traits
    by an effect, by suspending this Tamer, that Digimon gains \uFF1CRush\uFF1E for
    the turn."
